lead_paragraph: Double Olympic champion Miruts Yifter of Ethiopia has died at the age of 72, the International Association of Athletics Federations said on its website (www.iaaf.org) on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Double Olympic Champion Yifter Dies, Aged 72
